00:07:39.510 --> 00:07:41.410
in the name of comics,
he will respond.

00:07:41.410 --> 00:07:42.720
He will be there.

00:07:42.720 --> 00:07:44.070
He's a voice.

00:07:44.070 --> 00:07:47.040
You know? So, it's fantastic.

