00:07:55.710 --> 00:07:57.390
That's my goal.

00:07:57.390 --> 00:07:58.690
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: I met your wife.

00:07:58.690 --> 00:07:59.990
It's not going to happen.

00:07:59.990 --> 00:08:05.110
She-- because she's too smart
to fall for that, right?

00:08:05.110 --> 00:08:07.030
But-- and your kids right?

00:08:07.030 --> 00:08:08.330
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang: Oh, yeah.

00:08:08.330 --> 00:08:11.310
Yeah. Anybody you see on a
