00:08:11.310 --> 00:08:12.610
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: And,
well, and I don't know

00:08:12.610 --> 00:08:14.310
about you praising your
family because that came

00:08:14.310 --> 00:08:18.550
with a $625,000 no
strings attached grant.

00:08:18.550 --> 00:08:21.640
The one string is just to
support people who support comics.

00:08:21.640 --> 00:08:24.280
You know? But, you know,
I wanted to ask you--

00:08:24.280 --> 00:08:27.470
so, in January, you were
inaugurated as the ambassador.

00:08:27.470 --> 00:08:30.720
You're used to-- you spent
your career in schools.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.140
Now you get to go to schools.

00:08:32.140 --> 00:08:35.650
You get to spread the Gospel
while you're still creating.

00:08:35.650 --> 00:08:37.060
How are you finding it?

00:08:37.060 --> 00:08:38.360
You know, it's a little bit

00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:41.280
like winning an intellectual Miss
Universe where you have to show

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:45.890
up at so many functions, wear
the sash, but in the name

00:08:45.890 --> 00:08:48.860
of graphic novels, in the names
