Superman now.

00:11:14.270 --> 00:11:15.570
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang: Yeah,
it's kind of crazy.

00:11:15.570 --> 00:11:16.870
It's a really crazy thing.

00:11:16.870 --> 00:11:18.170
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Do you
ever pinch yourself and--

00:11:18.170 --> 00:11:19.470
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang: Absolutely.

00:11:19.470 --> 00:11:22.000
Yeah. I think-- it's unbelievable.

00:11:22.000 --> 00:11:23.300
It's unbelievable.

00:11:23.300 --> 00:11:25.780
I think if I had-- if
I could go back in time

00:11:25.780 --> 00:11:30.720 position:56%
