question for the gatekeeper.

00:16:26.300 --> 00:16:27.600
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Yeah.

00:16:27.600 --> 00:16:28.900
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang: Right?

00:16:28.900 --> 00:16:30.200
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: There
is the page and the pen.

00:16:30.200 --> 00:16:31.500
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang Yeah, absolutely.

00:16:31.500 --> 00:16:32.800
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: What we're
seeing on the page is the mirror

00:16:32.800 --> 00:16:34.520
and then what we can't see, who is
