00:16:34.520 --> 00:16:35.820
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang: Yes.

00:16:35.820 --> 00:16:37.120
&gt;&gt; Michael Cavna: Yeah.

00:16:37.120 --> 00:16:38.420
&gt;&gt; Gene Luen Yang: Exactly.

00:16:38.420 --> 00:16:39.720
So, I do think from the
